# Cursor Plans File Naming

## Requirement

Plan file names SHALL be descriptive of what the plan is doing. The name should clearly indicate the purpose and scope of the plan.

## Rationale

Descriptive file names ensure:
- Easy identification of plan purpose
- Quick understanding of plan scope
- Better organization when multiple plans exist
- Clear communication of intent to team members
- Easier navigation of planning history

